These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, apricot, eggplant, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, magic-tricks, fishing, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, western, martial-arts, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, ambient, rock, reggae
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, goldfish, pony
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the fan of soul is the person eating orange##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating orange##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching western movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | apricot    | eggplant      | orange  | grapes     |
| Hobby         | dancing    | fishing   | collecting | magic-tricks      |
| Movie-Genre   | western       | crime | martial-arts     | action    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | ambient         | soul  | rock    |
| Pet           | goldfish      | pony       | ferret | hamster |

