.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, sprite, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, crime, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, classical, techno
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, goat, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, ice-hockey, climbing
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of techno##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is the fan of classical##1
10. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk      | juice     | sprite    | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | adventure   | crime   | mystery           |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | techno     | classical    | punk         |
| Pet           | frog         | chinchilla | goat     | fish        |
| Sport         | swimming     | climbing  | lacrosse | ice-hockey       |

