.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, pear, watermelon, peas
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, indonesian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, chinchilla, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, badminton, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, bus, ship
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 6. the person driving the ship is the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the malaysian is the owner of the pony##1
10. the spanish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | lime    | peas      | watermelon  | pear   |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | indonesian      | spanish | brazilian      |
| Pet           | pony       | lizard         | cat  | chinchilla         |
| Sport         | cycling | handball | badminton  | surfing |
| Transport     | bus       | boat         | ship   | jet-ski        |

