.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, fanta, juice
There 4 different types of food: apple, apricot, plum, papaya
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, american, french
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, rat, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, train, tram
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the french is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating papaya is on the right of the american##1
 9. the argentine is on the left of the person eating apple##1
10. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta   | juice   | almond-milk      | water     |
| Food          | plum     | apple   | papaya | apricot |
| Nationality   | argentine | american | canadian   | french       |
| Pet           | goldfish       | hamster      | rabbit     | rat |
| Transport     | motorbike    | train     | tram     | airplane     |

