 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 3. the colombian is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is the person eating onion##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the engineer is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the owner of the fish is the pilot##1
 9. the person eating apricot is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the software-developer is on the far left##1
13. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
14. the malaysian is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
