The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, volleyball, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bike, car, ship
 1. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 5. the fisherman is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person drinking juice is the architect##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking tea##1
11. the bartender is on the left of the architect##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
