.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, soy-milk, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, chess, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, animation, action
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, italian, german
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, pony, frog
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the german is on the left of the japanese##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the owner of the fish is the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | soy-milk      | 7up      | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby         | cooking | chess | skydiving | traveling  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | zombie     | action      | satire |
| Nationality   | italian  | german     | japanese    | egyptian  |
| Pet           | fish  | frog       | rabbit          | pony      |

