.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pepper, corn, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, time-travel, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, baseball, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, train, trike
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating corn##1
11. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | lemon      | pepper     | grapes        | corn     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking     | baking    | dancing | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | time-travel  | comedy      | satire       |
| Sport         | baseball      | cycling | sailing     | rugby        |
| Transport     | train   | trike     | airplane  | scooter       |

