.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pomegranate, mango, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, puzzles, gardening, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher, lawyer, architect
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, ferret, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, bike, jet-ski
 1. the architect is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 3. the architect is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the mechanic##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the teacher##1
 8. the mechanic is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person eating mango is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person eating avocado is the owner of the hamster##1
11. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | pomegranate    | avocado        | orange        | mango      |
| Hobby       | gardening       | woodworking       | puzzles      | singing |
| Job         | teacher | architect | lawyer | mechanic      |
| Pet         | pony          | hamster         | rabbit           | ferret    |
| Transport   | bike         | subway       | jet-ski     | skateboard   |

 